<p>The <b>Thunder Stone</b> (Japanese: <b>かみなりのいし</b> <i>Lightning Stone</i>), formatted <b>Thunderstone</b> prior to <a href="/wiki/Generation_VI" title="Generation VI">Generation VI</a>, is a type of <a href="/wiki/Evolution_stone" class="mw-redirect" title="Evolution stone">Evolution stone</a> introduced in <a href="/wiki/Generation_I" title="Generation I">Generation I</a>.
</p>
