<p>In the <a href="/wiki/Generation_V" title="Generation V">Generation V</a> games, the Thunderstone can be sold to an <a href="/wiki/Item_maniac" title="Item maniac">item maniac</a> inside the <a href="/wiki/Icirrus_City" title="Icirrus City">Icirrus City</a> <a href="/wiki/Pok%C3%A9mon_Center" title="Pokémon Center">Pokémon Center</a> for <a href="/wiki/Pok%C3%A9mon_Dollar" title="Pokémon Dollar"><img alt="PokémonDollar.png" src="//cdn.bulbagarden.net/upload/8/8c/Pok%C3%A9monDollar.png" width="7" height="14" /></a>3000.
</p>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Effect">Effect</span></h3>
<p>Can be used to evolve one of several Pokémon. This consumes the Thunder Stone.
</p>
<ul><li>Causes <a href="/wiki/Pikachu_(Pok%C3%A9mon)" title="Pikachu (Pokémon)">Pikachu</a> to evolve into <a href="/wiki/Raichu_(Pok%C3%A9mon)" title="Raichu (Pokémon)">Raichu</a> (outside of <a href="/wiki/Alola" title="Alola">Alola</a>) or <a href="/wiki/Regional_variant" title="Regional variant">Alolan</a> <a href="/wiki/Raichu_(Pok%C3%A9mon)" title="Raichu (Pokémon)">Raichu</a> (in Alola)</li>
<li>Causes <a href="/wiki/Eevee_(Pok%C3%A9mon)" title="Eevee (Pokémon)">Eevee</a> to evolve into <a href="/wiki/Jolteon_(Pok%C3%A9mon)" title="Jolteon (Pokémon)">Jolteon</a></li>
<li>Causes <a href="/wiki/Eelektrik_(Pok%C3%A9mon)" title="Eelektrik (Pokémon)">Eelektrik</a> to evolve into <a href="/wiki/Eelektross_(Pok%C3%A9mon)" title="Eelektross (Pokémon)">Eelektross</a></li></ul>
