<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="In_spin-off_games">In spin-off games</span></h2>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Pok.C3.A9mon_Mystery_Dungeon_series">Pokémon Mystery Dungeon series</span></h3>
<p>The Thunderstone appears in <a href="/wiki/Pok%C3%A9mon_Mystery_Dungeon:_Red_Rescue_Team_and_Blue_Rescue_Team" title="Pokémon Mystery Dungeon: Red Rescue Team and Blue Rescue Team">Pokémon Mystery Dungeon: Red Rescue Team and Blue Rescue Team</a> and <a href="/wiki/Pok%C3%A9mon_Mystery_Dungeon" class="mw-disambig" title="Pokémon Mystery Dungeon">Pokémon Mystery Dungeon</a>: <a href="/wiki/Pok%C3%A9mon_Mystery_Dungeon:_Explorers_of_Time_and_Explorers_of_Darkness" title="Pokémon Mystery Dungeon: Explorers of Time and Explorers of Darkness">Explorers of Time, Explorers of Darkness</a>, and <a href="/wiki/Pok%C3%A9mon_Mystery_Dungeon:_Explorers_of_Sky" title="Pokémon Mystery Dungeon: Explorers of Sky">Explorers of Sky</a>.
</p>
