<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Pok.C3.A9mon_Conquest">Pokémon Conquest</span></h3>
<p>In <a href="/wiki/Pok%C3%A9mon_Conquest" title="Pokémon Conquest">Pokémon Conquest</a>, <a href="/wiki/Pikachu_(Pok%C3%A9mon)" title="Pikachu (Pokémon)">Pikachu</a> and <a href="/wiki/Eevee_(Pok%C3%A9mon)" title="Eevee (Pokémon)">Eevee</a> evolve into <a href="/wiki/Raichu_(Pok%C3%A9mon)" title="Raichu (Pokémon)">Raichu</a> and <a href="/wiki/Jolteon_(Pok%C3%A9mon)" title="Jolteon (Pokémon)">Jolteon</a>, respectively, if their <a href="/wiki/Link" title="Link">link</a> is improved while their <a href="/wiki/Warrior" title="Warrior">Warrior</a> is equipped with a Thunderstone.
</p><p>A Thunderstone can be purchased from the <a href="/wiki/Pok%C3%A9mon_Conquest#Traveling_merchant" title="Pokémon Conquest">traveling merchant</a> for 5000 gold, and sold for 2500-3250 gold.
</p>
<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Description_3">Description</span></h4>
<table width="60%" style="background: #D880A8; border-radius: 10px; -moz-border-radius: 10px; -webkit-border-radius: 10px; -khtml-border-radius: 10px; -icab-border-radius: 10px; -o-border-radius: 10px;; border: 5px solid #C86890;">

<tr>
<td>
<table border="1" width="100%" style="background: #FFFFFF; border:1px solid #D880A8; border-collapse:collapse;">

